com.datastrato.gravitino.client

Class GravitinoMetaLake

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datastrato.gravitino.dto.MetalakeDTO
      • com.datastrato.gravitino.client.GravitinoMetaLake
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Auditable, Metalake, SupportsCatalogs

    public class GravitinoMetaLake
extends MetalakeDTO
implements SupportsCatalogs
    Gravitino Metalake is the top-level metadata repository for users. It contains a list of catalogs as sub-level metadata collections. With GravitinoMetaLake, users can list, create, load, alter and drop a catalog with specified identifier.
